{"word":"Nebuchadnezzar","slug":"nebuchadnezzar","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Nebuchadnezzar</b> <a href=\"#/H5020\">H5020</a> <br/> Called also Nebuchadrezzar.<br/> King of Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=21&verse=2'>Jer 21:2</a><br/> Empire of<br/> <a href='S:Babylon'>Babylon</a><br/> His administration<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1'>Dan 1</a><br/> Conquests of:<br/> - Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=24'>2Ki 24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=15'>1Ch 6:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=36&verse=21'>2Ch 36:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=1&verse=7'>Ezr 1:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=39'>Jer 39</a> <br/> - Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=24&verse=7'>2Ki 24:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=2'>Jer 46:2</a> <br/> - Tyre<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=29&verse=18'>Eze 29:18</a> <br/> An instrument of God's judgments<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=27&verse=8'>Jer 27:8</a><br/> Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=21&verse=7'>Jer 21:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=21&verse=10'>Jer 21:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=22&verse=25'>Jer 22:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=25&verse=9'>Jer 25:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=27&verse=9'>Jer 27:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=32&verse=28'>Jer 32:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=43&verse=10'>Jer 43:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=13'>Jer 46:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=33'>Jer 49:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=26&verse=12'>Eze 26:12</a>"}]}